    29)------------------------TableScan: partsupp projection=[ps_partkey, ps_suppkey, ps_supplycost]
    30)------------------------TableScan: supplier projection=[s_suppkey, s_nationkey]
    31)--------------------TableScan: nation projection=[n_nationkey, n_regionkey]
    32)----------------Projection: region.r_regionkey
    33)------------------Filter: region.r_name = Utf8View("EUROPE")
    34)--------------------TableScan: region projection=[r_regionkey, r_name], partial_filters=[region.r_name = Utf8View("EUROPE")]
